structure.unit: JUVENILE PROCEEDINGS -- COMMITMENT AND CARE OF CHILDREN

law.history: Repealed 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 423, sec. 198, effective July 1, 1987. -- Amended 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 92, sec. 68, effective June 18, 1970. -- Amended 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 157, sec. 29, effective February 27, 1956. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 22, effective January 1, 1953.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Department for human resources may assist juvenile courts in placing children -- County contributions.
metadata.note: This section was repealed by 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 280, which was to have become effective July 1, 1982. Thereafter, 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 284 changed the effective date of that act to July 15, 1984. Then, 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 184 repealed both 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 280, and 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 284.
